The tiny Kingdom of Glavia, nestled in the shadow of 
the great mountains of the north between two mighty 
rivers, has been beset by an invasion of demons. Once 
you have restored the King to his throne, help him rid
Glavia of the demon menace. Visit him in the throne room 
for more details.

This is a difficult quest, however, there are many items 
you may find on the way which will help you in more than 
just the quest. Therefore, it may be worth your while to 
start now.

Note: you *will* need a helping hand during at least one 
part of the quest. Additionally, look at everything in 
detail, and use your other senses as well. Treat the area 
as you would the real world: actions have effects that may 
range far from your immediate vicinity. Logic should tell 
you what *should* happen when you try something, and for
the most part, it will.

You must complete Forgetful King before you may complete 
this quest.
